prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: Well we have a annual family get together now for the last 5 years. On Fathers day I have a bbq  and invite my sons family over. My grandson has his birthday shortly after Fathers Day so we combine the two. We had so much fun with the kids and having everyone over also. I have a younger grandson his brother, and we have a yard bbq party for him also now in August. Last time he got a helium balloon  for him and I and he accidently released ir.
